    <h2>・第12課：シオンの大義の確立　[Cause of Zion]</h2>
    <p> ============================== </p>
    <img src="https://www.churchofjesuschrist.org/imgs/23abd9265703691299082c0289a02b942c854924/full/%211600%2C/0/default"
